metadata.name: Body Part(y)
metadata.description:
A playful and psychedelic NFT, Body Part(y) illustrates androgynous figures whose body parts come together in a fit of ecstatic pleasure celebrating unadulterated hedonism and the beauty of the human form.

Generated using AI and refined by the artist Cat Citrine, this artwork is inspired by the excesses and eclectic gatherings of the 1960s' Summer of Love—when uninhibited crowds came to San Francisco's Haight-Ashbury district in droves, eager to partake in all that counterculture had to offer.

Dimensions: 1920 × 1920
Format: MP4
